  ],
  "remarks": "Minister for Planning and Finance in Colonel Qadhafi’s Government. Involved in violence against demonstrators. Secretary of the General People’s Committee for Finance and Planning. Zltini is currently acting as temporary head of the Central Bank of Libya. He was previously National Oil Corporation Chairman. Our information suggests that he is currently engaged in trying to raise funds for the regime to replenish Central Bank reserves already spent on sustaining the current military campaign.",
